encodingDesc.p:
For the purposes of the HyperStack, Bieler’s
                 edition has been deeply encoded digitally, along with its entire academic framework;
                 that is, with its threefold apparatus, namely:


- the apparatus criticus, indicating all
                 variant readings in the manuscripts and emendations;

- the apparatus fontium, indicating
                 sources and parallel text traditions;

- the apparatus biblicus, indicating biblical
                 references to specific bible versions.

